data.description: Luxury Living in Milford Ponds!  Upgraded Single level home with Pond Views.   Prepare to be captivated by this stunning single-family home that epitomizes modern comfort and style.   Located in Milford Ponds, this Like New gem offers a harmonious blend of elegance and convenience, complete with multiple upgrades and tranquil pond views.  Enjoy the amenities of Milford Ponds including the community swimming pool, walking trails and a club house with a fitness center.  Situated on a lot which features a fenced in backyard, a maintenance free Trex deck with retractable awning and views of the pond, fountain and community swimming pool.  The heart of this home is undoubtedly the upgraded kitchen.   Boasting exquisite white cabinets, backsplash, luxurious granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a built-in air-purifier.   Experience the convenience of first floor living featuring LVP flooring throughout, 36" doorways and hallway, grab bars in both bathrooms and a large walk-in closet located within the master bedroom.   Enjoy the benefits of a tankless hot water heater, which provides energy efficiency and an endless supply of hot water for your family's needs.   Conveniently located near restaurants, shopping, downtown Milford and the local beaches.   Schedue your showing today!
